oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hatch Show Print May We Suggest Card
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Hatch Show Print (Firm); Offset printing; Roosters;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color card (red on white) advertising Hatch Show Print. The card contains the phrase, "May we suggest you order your posters from Hatch Show Print," along with the Hatch "We Crow About Our Prompt Service" logo with roosters and the shop's address. It is possible that this card was printed on the offset press.
